channel.title: Satan's Fury Clan! [SFRC] The newest Clan to rs!
channel.description:
Hello, Of course this is my RS Clan. It will one day hopefully be a very popular Clan. ATM we have just a clan that posts pictures Pkz, Cwars, and more.
But Soon we will have a clan that is divided in to 3.
1st group will be: Legendary Clan Member
2nd group will be: Normal Clan Member
3rd group will be: Newbie Clan Member
well thats all later when we get some more members.
Well if you want to join go to this site: http://satansfury.rs2status.com/
